Author: LemoChain
Title: (ANN)(LEMO) LemoChain - Business Data Circulation Infrastructure - ICO APRIL 2ND
Body: https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505732/bitcointalk/Lemo_01.jpg https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505731/bitcointalk/Lemo_02.jpg https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505731/bitcointalk/Lemo_03.jpg https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505732/bitcointalk/Lemo_04.png https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505732/bitcointalk/Lemo_05.png https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505733/bitcointalk/Lemo_06.png https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505734/bitcointalk/Lemo_07.png https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505734/bitcointalk/Lemo_08.png https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505732/bitcointalk/Lemo_09.png https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505732/bitcointalk/Lemo_10.png https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505732/bitcointalk/Lemo_11.png https://res.cloudinary.com/lnky/image/upload/v1520505731/bitcointalk/Lemo_12.jpg Twitter  Telegram  Facebook  Reddit   LemoChain is a decentralised, open source platform for business data circulation. LemoChain, founded by the non-profit Lemo Foundation, aims to reduce the technological distance between blockchain technology and common commercial logic.   Through delivering an easily accessible  platform for businesses of all sizes to monetise and exchange their data, we aim to accelerate blockchain’s integration into our every-day lives by means of increasing it’s universal commercial relevance.  LemoChain also serves to reduce the current data oligopoly, by creating a level playing field for any business to access this invaluable resource being coined as ‘the new oil’.  Our end goal is to make all businesses significantly more competitive through simplified data access and the opportunity for a new profit channel, via data monetisation.    ICO Start: 02/04/2018 ICO End: 09/04/2018   Token Platform: ERC-20  Token Supply:  Total 1.6bn LEMO (45% offered to investors)  Fundraising Target:  Hard Cap: 16,666 ETH Soft Cap: 1,666 ETH   Country of Origin: Singapore  Social Media:  Telegram:  https://t.me/lemochain Twitter:  https://twitter.com/LemoChain Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LemoChain/ Medium: https://medium.com/@lemochain Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/user/LemoChain/
